{"tid":2151591,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日本3猛男移居無人島避疫","createTime":"2020-08-11T12:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T14:55:58.000Z","uid":153217,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d084dbc4565b06d6db22534f23dddb3797461015","tid":2151591,"uid":153217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:49:34.000Z","msg":"日本3猛男移居無人島避疫 捉魚燒柴過原始生活<br />\n<br />\n這次不談論玄學,  只為分享在世上別人的生活<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AypROh4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAypROh4.jpg&h=397c1334&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎持續肆虐，疫情下大家都減少外出，避免與太多人接觸。不過日本有位猛男最近夥同友人，移居到九州一個無人島，表示早前因政府頒布緊急狀態令，多個設施暫停開放，於是決定暫離城市，找尋一個杳無人煙的地方呼吸新鮮空氣。他們更拍片紀錄每日生活，無論撿柴生火、起帳篷，或是煮食等，亦一手包辦，至今已住足1個月，猶如上演&ldquo;真人版動森&rdquo;！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LL37mC7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLL37mC7.jpg&h=372daa59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱愛大自然的日男Ken，不時會參與戶外活動如露營及潛水，今年4月中他與2位朋友挑戰移居九州一無人島，表示在疫情下想找個地方&ldquo;喘一口氣&rdquo;，於是決定只帶魚竿、魚叉、鋸子、帳篷、廚具、充電器、調味料，以及一隻活雞，就開展了野外&ldquo;新生活&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HGf9zYi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHGf9zYi.jpg&h=83d62f71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tpNgeYm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtpNgeYm.jpg&h=1ee59e24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n他們在Twitter及YouTube記錄每日生活狀況，由找地方築起帳篷至撿柴起火都由3人合力慢慢完成。他們更會潛水活捉鯛魚等海魚，甚至是體型較大的吞拿魚。由於只有少量廚具，他們指最方便的食法就是切成刺身或是煮成火鍋，更大贊在大自然生活，最好的是能嚐到最新鮮的食材。<br />\n<br />\n不過Ken曾於片中稱，因為&ldquo;居住&rdquo;的地方臨海，不只會起大風，有時下雨或潮漲更會吹走帳篷，非常麻煩。因此後來3人決定搬到島上一洞穴居住，為了配合環境，他們更於片中扮成原始人，只用葉子遮住下體，非常爆笑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U2MT1Dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU2MT1Dd.jpg&h=a77644b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3人的島上生活引來網民討論，紛紛讚歎他們夠大膽，能在島上自給自足，亦有人笑言像是近期爆紅的遊戲《動物之森》真人版，留言鼓勵他們堅持下去，&ldquo;愛看你們的生活影片，請繼續加油&rdquo;、&ldquo;你們很厲害&rdquo;、&ldquo;不就是動森的生活嗎&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n目前已住滿1個月的他們指，會繼續野外生活，直至疫情完結。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ken_osak?lang=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fken_osak%3Flang%3Den&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9Fs0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=80bb35c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ken_osak?lang=en</a>"},{"pid":"10dff7be140480086fbf7e8fdfbcac6461983fde","tid":2151591,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:53:52.000Z","msg":"old news"},{"pid":"58eaa39d16b920fbe56f5e71310dc1ffe44802a7","tid":2151591,"uid":195136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:54:40.000Z","msg":"3個無女朋友的毒撚"},{"pid":"7521a59c2f52b705bb9d0bce4573a9961e7c9aee","tid":2151591,"uid":20099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:55:57.000Z","msg":"點解唔係一男兩女..."},{"pid":"7c543f3d98450f89671ae376551ce5abb13f468f","tid":2151591,"uid":333199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:56:11.000Z","msg":"GAY!"},{"pid":"82c891ee47b79b12bb3642a42f43411915a898ab","tid":2151591,"uid":333199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:56:48.000Z","msg":"一定有玩圍圈圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8924285f7087af692923759e7d0deeb0a287c903","tid":2151591,"uid":85965,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:58:20.000Z","msg":"點upload片??"},{"pid":"83c6efe15d296024302af5d64569bffba6231a7c","tid":2151591,"uid":15592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:59:26.000Z","msg":"真人動森"},{"pid":"f1d6d8fa5988c3055fca83a9093695110151de04","tid":2151591,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:01:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"443ac61d16b0691a54226e46509aa8d84cebb18c"